1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:10,488
HAIDER: We can take him down, Iqra. I've been watching Hadi's racing schedule, we know exactly when and where he'll be.

2
00:00:10,488 --> 00:00:14,688
IQRASH: But are we sure he's the one we want? What if he's not as weak as he seems?

3
00:00:14,688 --> 00:00:20,256
HAIDER: He's our only chance at redemption, Iqra. We can't let him get away.

4
00:00:20,256 --> 00:00:26,554
HAMMAD: Hey, guys, I couldn't help but overhear. Why don't we settle this like men, in the upcoming annual car race?

5
00:00:26,554 --> 00:00:32,434
HAIDER: You think you're funny, don't you, Hammad? Trying to turn this into some joke.

6
00:00:32,434 --> 00:00:37,378
HAMMAD: Not at all, my friend. I just think it's time we put our skills to the test.

7
00:00:37,378 --> 00:00:40,700
HADI: Come on, baby, just a little more power...

8
00:00:40,700 --> 00:00:44,612
HADI: I can do this. I have to do this.

9
00:00:44,612 --> 00:00:47,262
HAIDER: Let's show him what we're made of, Iqra!

10
00:00:47,262 --> 00:00:49,854
IQRASH: You got this, Haider. We're in this together.

11
00:00:49,854 --> 00:00:53,200
HAIDER: What the...? How did he do that?

12
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:57,434
HAIDER: Congratulations, Hadi. You won this time.

13
00:00:57,434 --> 00:01:01,826
HADI: Thanks, Haider. But it's not over yet.
